name: WOO Network
public_notice: Wootrade Network has rebranded to WOO Network. For more information, please read https://medium.com/woonetwork/new-names-new-logos-how-woo-network-is-changing-markets-as-we-know-them-575ed472b0d9

description.en: WOO Network is a deep liquidity network connecting traders, exchanges, institutions, and DeFi platforms with democratized access to the best-in-class liquidity and trading execution at lower or zero cost. WOO Token is used in the network’s CeFi and DeFi products for staking and fee discounts.
